http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.@value: MARC Code List for Relators Scheme

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.@value: Relator terms and their associated codes designate the relationship between a name and a bibliographic resource. The relator codes are three-character lowercase alphabetic strings that serve as identifiers. Either the term or the code may be used as controlled values.
